## Code Conventions

- Code comments: English
- Variable/function names: English
- UI strings: Use l10n (ARB files), do not hardcode
- Commits: Conventional Commits format (`feat:`, `fix:`, `docs:`, `refactor:`)
- No emojis in code unless explicitly requested

## Key Patterns

### Riverpod Provider Pattern
```dart
@riverpod
class FeedNotifier extends _$FeedNotifier {
  @override
  FutureOr<List<Article>> build() async { ... }
  Future<void> loadMore() async { ... }
}
```

### Freezed Model Pattern
```dart
@freezed
sealed class Article with _$Article {
  const factory Article({required String id, ...}) = _Article;
  factory Article.fromJson(Map<String, dynamic> json) => _$ArticleFromJson(json);
}
```

### Dio Interceptor Pattern
```dart
class AuthInterceptor extends Interceptor {
  @override
  void onRequest(RequestOptions options, RequestInterceptorHandler handler) { ... }
  @override
  Future<void> onError(DioException err, ErrorInterceptorHandler handler) async { ... }
}
```
